room_title: Escape room "Wild West" by Amazing Escape Room in Freehold
review: My family and I did the Wild Wild West room and loved it! We made it out with a few minutes to spare. Great way to.celebrate my dad's 60th!

room_title: Escape room "Wild West" by Amazing Escape Room in Freehold
review: Five of us went on Thanksgiving Eve. It was our first Escape Room experience. There was one point where a clue we revealed was in the wrong box...but we got 2 minutes added on. We made it out in 35 minutes, and were pretty excited about it. The staff was super nice, helpful, and seemed to like what they were doing. We'll be back for sure.

room_title: Escape room "Wild West" by Amazing Escape Room in Freehold
review: Such a great place to get your mind working! My best friends and I went for their birthday and we had such a blast! Totally worth going to any chance you get!
